The Philippines' trade deficit widened to542 mln dlrs in the eight months to end-August from 159 mlndlrs in the same 1986 period, the National Statistics Officesaid.    It said exports in the eight-month period rose to 3.58billion dlrs from 3.18 billion in 1986, while imports rose to4.12 billion dlrs from 3.34 billion a year earlier.    The country's trade deficit totalled 202 mln dlrs in 1986. REUTER&#3;